title: NCH Switch 4.65 + Patch [SWEG]
description:
Includes the NCH Switch v4.65 installation package, a patch and a text file containing instructions.

Install as usual. After installation use the provided patch. No serial number required. Done! Enjoy!

NCH Switch is a "universal" audio converter that supports all popular formats. With it you can convert to and from many formats and extract audio from video files. Batch conversions, even thousands of files, are easily handled by Switch.


FEATURES:

-Automatically normalize audio levels
-ID3 tags are preserved for supporting formats
-Access online database to add song information
-Play audio tracks prior to conversion
-Import and convert playlists (.m3u and .pls)
-Extract audio from imported videos or DVD
-Batch convert thousands of files at once
-Optimized CPU usage for fast conversion
